      • getNearPrice

        public double getNearPrice()
        Returns:
        nearPrice What the starting price would be if the market was reconciled now taking into account the SP bets as well as unmatched exchange bets on the same selection in the exchange.

      • getFarPrice

        public double getFarPrice()
        Returns:
        farPrice What the starting price would be if the market was reconciled now taking into account only the currently place SP bets. The Far Price is not as complicated but not as accurate and only accounts for money on the exchange at SP.
